Package com.atakmap.coremap.conversions

Class ConversionFactors

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.coremap.conversions.ConversionFactors
  • public class ConversionFactors
extends java.lang.Object
    Centralized location for conversion factors. Distance conversion factors obtained from the SpanUtilities. Most of these conversion factors were pulled from tables such as https://www.wsdot.wa.gov/Reference/metrics/factors.htm or conversion.org
